@node History "AmiGOD - Historia"

				@{b}Historia@{ub}
				========


AmiGOD 1.50 (26/12/2001)
========================
- fixed some gui problems (in database & after tests)
- rewritten box & pixel routines - 24% speed up (AGA), smaller code
- database : 80 test-results from amigists all over the world!
- dodana wersja jëzykowa 'PORTUGUESE' - podziëkowania dla Raul Silva, dziëki
- dodana wersja jëzykowa 'RUSSIAN' - podziëkowania dla Vadim Vlasenko, dziëki
  10 supported languages  (czech, deutsch, english, francais, italiano,
  magyar, polski, portuguese, russian, slovak)
- new identify.library
- added new identify.library installation script by me
- recompiled in AmiBlitz2, smaller code
- nowe screenshoty, dziëki

10/2001 -> now I'm very very very very very busy, bad university :-((
10/2001 -> developing of AmiGOD v2 must be paused :-(
09/2001 -> AmiGOD 2.00 beta 1 written in C -> 6 graphical tests
09/2001 -> now I'm learning language C, be patient please (maybe AmiGOD2 :-))

(1.45+)

AmiGOD 1.45 (07/07/2001)
========================
- fixed Print Text bug
- new results, thanks

